  "text": "where H(\u00b7) and g(\u00b7) are the Hessian matrix and the gradient vector of (6) with respect to \u03b8, respectively, and their analytical forms are found in [CITATION_1] . Upon convergence of the iteration, the MD measurement is computed by",
